    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Put a little Seoul in your mid-week dinner. For an extra kick, you'll pan-fry shredded tofu in spicy-sweet gochujang until perfectly crispy before serving it up with a crunchy sweet pea pods, lettuce and rice salad. Under 600 calories.",
